# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:9
translate chinese u19a2s1c_a9a112e9:

    # "Feeling this strange tug, almost like Dana is calling to me, I walk down the path towards her voice."
    "我感到一种奇怪的牵引，仿佛达娜在呼唤我，于是沿着声音传来的方向走去。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:12
translate chinese u19a2s1c_e8c9af55:

    # "Eventually, I reach a clearing with a tall stone tower rising up at least 100 feet above me."
    "最终，我来到一片空地，一座高耸的石塔矗立在眼前，足有100英尺高。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:13
translate chinese u19a2s1c_4cc65452:

    # "As I walk closer to it, I begin to hear a sound coming from inside. A woman sobbing."
    "走近塔楼时，我开始听到里面传来的声音。一个女人在抽泣。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:16
translate chinese u19a2s1c_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "“有人吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:17
translate chinese u19a2s1c_e7263129:

    # "I call out, wondering if whoever is inside would even hear me over their crying."
    "我喊道，心想里面的人在哭泣声中是否能听见我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:18
translate chinese u19a2s1c_265a0522:

    # "Then I hear a voice I recognize call back."
    "接着，我听见一个熟悉的声音回应。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:19
translate chinese u19a2s1c_cc59b48e:

    # cw "Hello? Is somebody out there?"
    cw "“有人吗？外面有人吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:20
translate chinese u19a2s1c_93e86f9e:

    # pc "Dana?"
    pc "“达娜？”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:24
translate chinese u19a2s1c_99c51cff:

    # "I step inside and find the place a mess, covered in filth, a putrid stench in the air. Moldy furs form a bed in the corner and a staircase rises to the second floor."
    "我走进塔内，发现这里一片狼藉，满地污秽，空气中弥漫着腐臭的气味。角落里堆着发霉的毛皮充当床铺，一架楼梯通向二楼。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:25
translate chinese u19a2s1c_cb391ba1:

    # "Dana is shackled to the wall, completely naked."
    "达娜被锁链拴在墙上，浑身赤裸。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:26
translate chinese u19a2s1c_2fef227d:

    # cw "Who's there? Please help."
    cw "“是谁？求求你救救我。”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:29
translate chinese u19a2s1c_392b8d63:

    # pc "Dana? What's happening? Who did this to you?"
    pc "“达娜？怎么回事？是谁对你做了这种事？”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:30
translate chinese u19a2s1c_d209c8cd:

    # cw "My betrothed, Terry."
    cw "“是我的未婚夫，特里。”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:31
translate chinese u19a2s1c_19dbdea6:

    # pc "Ugh, that fucker."
    pc "“呸，那个混蛋。”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:32
translate chinese u19a2s1c_8ccecee9:

    # cw "Who are you? How did you know my name?"
    cw "“你是谁？你怎么知道我的名字？”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:35
translate chinese u19a2s1c_1911c327:

    # pc "My name is [pcname]... and that's a long story. Where's the key to these things?"
    pc "“我叫[pcname]……这说来话长。这些锁链的钥匙在哪儿？”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:36
translate chinese u19a2s1c_c3f9873f:

    # cw "Terry has it."
    cw "“特里拿着。”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:37
translate chinese u19a2s1c_b3138b62:

    # pc "Well where is he, so I can knock him out and get it back?"
    pc "那他在哪儿？我好把他打晕，把钥匙拿回来。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:40
translate chinese u19a2s1c_51c802e4:

    # cw "You must be a great warrior to think that you can fight Terry the Troll."
    cw "你一定是个了不起的战士，居然觉得自己能打败巨魔特里。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:41
translate chinese u19a2s1c_d473561c:

    # pc "The Troll? How big of a troll are we talking here?"
    pc "巨魔？我们说的是多大的巨魔？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:42
translate chinese u19a2s1c_1dc43d34:

    # pc "Like, \"Little naked baby with neon hair that sticks up\" troll, or like \"They have a cave troll?\" troll, or like \"Troll in the dungeon!\" troll?"
    pc "是那种“头发像霓虹灯一样竖着的小光屁股宝宝”巨魔，还是“他们有洞穴巨魔？”那种，还是“地牢里的巨魔！”那种？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:45
translate chinese u19a2s1c_b9ce964b:

    # "Just then, I feel the ground shake as something approaches."
    "就在这时，我感觉到地面震动，似乎有什么东西正在靠近。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:46
translate chinese u19a2s1c_d0853512:

    # cw "Um... he's big."
    cw "呃……他好大。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:49
translate chinese u19a2s1c_a0980239:

    # pc "So how do I get you out of here?"
    pc "那我该怎么把你弄出去？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:52
translate chinese u19a2s1c_7d360180:

    # cw "Hand me my spear and magic helmet."
    cw "把我的长矛和魔法头盔递给我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:55
translate chinese u19a2s1c_f825bf4b:

    # pc "Your spear and magic helmet?"
    pc "你的长矛和魔法头盔？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:58
translate chinese u19a2s1c_b5bce132:

    # cw "My spear and magic helmet."
    cw "我的长矛和魔法头盔。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:61
translate chinese u19a2s1c_60625aaa:

    # cw "They're right over there."
    cw "就在那边。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:64
translate chinese u19a2s1c_753fa59f:

    # "I quickly grab her spear and magic helmet and hand them to her, putting the spear in her hand and the helmet on her head."
    "我迅速抓起她的长矛和魔法头盔递给她，把长矛塞进她手里，把头盔戴在她头上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:67
translate chinese u19a2s1c_bb7c096e:

    # "As soon as she holds the spear and wears the helmet, I see power visibly coursing through her body and she flexes, shattering the shackles and pulling free from the wall."
    "她刚握住长矛、戴上头盔，我就看见力量明显地在她体内奔涌，她一挥手，镣铐瞬间碎裂，她从墙上挣脱出来。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:68
translate chinese u19a2s1c_36fa1894:

    # cw "Damn, that feels good."
    cw "该死，这感觉真爽。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:71
translate chinese u19a2s1c_b5ed8a35:

    # "Armor forms from nothingness and stitches itself around her body as she steps confidently towards the door."
    "当她自信地走向门口时，铠甲凭空形成，自动缝合在她身上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:72
translate chinese u19a2s1c_5c1e9a82:

    # cw "Let's get the hell out of here, [pcname]."
    cw "咱们赶紧从这儿滚出去吧，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:73
translate chinese u19a2s1c_3d2542f2:

    # pc "Good plan."
    pc "好主意。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:76
translate chinese u19a2s1c_c7622eec:

    # "We run together down the stairs and out of the tower, where a massive form is waiting for us."
    "我们并肩冲下楼梯，逃出塔楼，却发现一个庞然巨物正等在那里。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:77
translate chinese u19a2s1c_3cf50cd0:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}DANA! WHERE YOU GOING!? WHO THIS!?"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}达娜！你要去哪儿！？这是谁！？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:80
translate chinese u19a2s1c_95907875:

    # cw "You've kept me imprisoned for too long! I will never love you, Terry! I'm leaving!"
    cw "你把我囚禁太久了！我永远不会爱你，特里！我要走了！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:81
translate chinese u19a2s1c_37ca861b:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}NO! YOU NO CAN LEAVE! I NO LET YOU!"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}不！你不能走！我绝不让你走！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:84
translate chinese u19a2s1c_1b35b937:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}YOU MINE!"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}你是我的！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:85
translate chinese u19a2s1c_8b36aec6:

    # cw "Never!"
    cw "绝不！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:88
translate chinese u19a2s1c_760e15ee:

    # "With a power I never imagined, Dana leaps up into the air, holding her spear high and letting out a war cry."
    "达娜迸发出我从未想象过的力量，猛地跃入空中，高举长矛并发出战吼。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:91
translate chinese u19a2s1c_5fe8a156:

    # "She brings it down, stabbing it into the troll's massive shoulder."
    "她挥矛下刺，将矛尖刺入巨魔那宽厚的肩膀。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:92
translate chinese u19a2s1c_9df6a73f:

    # "She seems to be holding back though and the spear only barely pierces through the thick hide."
    "不过她似乎有所保留，长矛仅勉强刺穿了那层厚实的皮甲。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:95
translate chinese u19a2s1c_326ba2ba:

    # "It's enough though. As soon as the troll is wounded, he screams in pain."
    "但这已足够。巨魔刚一受伤，便痛得嚎叫起来。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:96
translate chinese u19a2s1c_f6d36d63:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}YOU HURT ME!"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}你伤到我了！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:97
translate chinese u19a2s1c_88c391e6:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}OWWWWWWWW!"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}呜哇哇哇哇哇！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:100
translate chinese u19a2s1c_e8ca8dba:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}YOU SO MEAN! I HATE YOU!"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}你太坏了！我恨你！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:101
translate chinese u19a2s1c_931afe25:

    # "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}WAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHH!"
    "Terry the Troll" "{size=*2.5}哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:104
translate chinese u19a2s1c_eff3e908:

    # pc "Well, that was easy."
    pc "嗯，这还真容易。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:105
translate chinese u19a2s1c_c40e8902:

    # cw "He's a big baby. If he didn't have me chained, I could have escaped a long time ago."
    cw "这家伙简直是个大宝宝。要不是被我锁着，我早就逃走了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:106
translate chinese u19a2s1c_6c986824:

    # pc "Why does he run like a Muppet though?"
    pc "不过他怎么跑得像个木偶呢？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:107
translate chinese u19a2s1c_6ecff0e2:

    # cw "What's a Muppet?"
    cw "什么是木偶？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:108
translate chinese u19a2s1c_59c8b59d:

    # pc "Nevermind."
    pc "算了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:109
translate chinese u19a2s1c_bd67da0a:

    # cw "Okay, well let's get out of here before he comes back. Where are you heading?"
    cw "好吧，趁他还没回来，咱们赶紧离开这儿。你要去哪儿？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:112
translate chinese u19a2s1c_cab5ada1:

    # pc "North. To the Ice Queen's castle."
    pc "去北方。去冰雪女王的城堡。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:113
translate chinese u19a2s1c_c37652cf:

    # cw "Great. Let's go!"
    cw "太好了。走吧！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:114
translate chinese u19a2s1c_cfed4f99:

    # pc "Just like that?"
    pc "就这样？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:115
translate chinese u19a2s1c_e13e5280:

    # cw "Just like that. You kind of saved my life. Wherever you go, I go."
    cw "就这样。你算是救了我一命。你去哪儿，我就去哪儿。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:118
translate chinese u19a2s1c_30f92a92:

    # cw "How did you know my name, anyways?"
    cw "话说回来，你怎么知道我的名字？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:119
translate chinese u19a2s1c_3514b6ef:

    # pc "That is a long story."
    pc "这说来话长。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:120
translate chinese u19a2s1c_4339842a:

    # cw "It's going to be a long walk."
    cw "这可是一段漫长的路程。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene1c.rpy:121
translate chinese u19a2s1c_447e77ae:

    # "We walk along together and I spend the rest of the day explaining to her everything about me being from another world, the bracelet, and the Ice Queen."
    "我们并肩而行，我花了一整天的时间向她解释我来自另一个世界、手镯以及冰雪女王的一切。"

